<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Kalvari Tang</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Awi hitiu aw, kalvari tang,
 I Lalpa tha a kiekna mun;
 Sietlei gitloh ziekin,
 Lal nunnem thakiek na
 Lal nunnem thakiek na

[V2]
 2. Tang chu ei tunin aw Lautha,
 Ka Lalpa liem thawkna mun chu;
 Ei pui tungin lautha,
 A pul ka do zo puoi
 A pul ka do zo puoi

[V3]
 3. Khulsina sambang zal dingin,
 Lalpa luong chu a chiehpih tau;
 Kapa zui a um puou,
 Lainat a um taluoi
 Lainat a um taluoi

[V4]
 4. A zalna khulsin muh ka nuom,
 Ka Lalpa luong a sielnau chu;
 A liengvai taluo ie,
 A thihni chan inle!
 A thihni chan inle !</lyrics>
<author>V.T Kappu</author>
<hymn_number>67</hymn_number>
</song>